{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UgkiCiUy7cy3Ym3ak4BfdA","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t# changebrief\n2\t\n3\tAI-powered regulatory monitoring. Watches government and agency websites, detects changes, and tells you *what* changed — not just that something changed.\n4\t\n5\t> \"Finansinspektionen published new capital adequacy requirements for credit institutions. Effective 2026-06-01.\"\n6\t\n7\t**Live:** [changebrief.io](https://changebrief.io) | **App:** [app.changebrief.io](https://app.changebrief.io) | **Status:** [app.changebrief.io/status](https://app.changebrief.io/status)\n8\t\n9\t## How it works\n10\t\n11\t1. **Playwright** screenshots each monitored page every 6 hours\n12\t2. **Pixelmatch** compares with previous screenshot (cheap pixel filter)\n13\t3. If change > threshold → **GPT-4o Vision** analyzes what changed\n14\t4. AI classifies regulatory changes: `action_required`, `review_recommended`, or `info_only`\n15\t5. Notifications via email, Slack, Teams, Discord, PagerDuty, or webhook\n16\t\n17\t## Architecture\n18\t\n19\t```\n20\tlanding/          — Astro + Tailwind → Cloudflare Pages (changebrief.io)\n21\tapp/              — Next.js (App Router) + Auth.js → Vercel (app.changebrief.io)\n22\tengine/           — Playwright + GPT-4o Vision → GitHub Actions (cron every 6h)\n23\tshared/           — Shared logic (diff, vision, notify, schema)\n24\ttests/            — Vitest test suite\n25\t```\n26\t\n27\t| Component | Tech | Where |\n28\t|---|---|---|\n29\t| Landing page | Astro + Tailwind | Cloudflare Pages |\n30\t| Web app | Next.js, Auth.js, Turso | Vercel |\n31\t| Database | Turso (libsql, eu-west-1) | AWS Ireland |\n32\t| Engine | Playwright, Pixelmatch, OpenAI | GitHub Actions |\n33\t| Billing | Polar.sh + Stripe | External |\n34\t| Email | Resend | External |\n35\t\n36\t## Getting started\n37\t\n38\t```bash\n39\t# 1. Clone and install\n40\tgit clone https://github.com/TWINDEJ/changebrief.git\n41\tcd changebrief\n42\tnpm install\n43\tnpx playwright install chromium\n44\t\n45\t# 2. Configure\n46\tcp .env.example .env\n47\t# Fill in all required variables (see .env.example for details)\n48\t\n49\t# 3. Run the app locally\n50\tcd app && npm install && npm run dev\n51\t\n52\t# 4. Run the engine manually\n53\tnpx ts-node engine/check-all.ts\n54\t```\n55\t\n56\t## Environment variables\n57\t\n58\tSee `.env.example` for the complete list. Required:\n59\t\n60\t| Variable | Purpose |\n61\t|---|---|\n62\t| `TURSO_DATABASE_URL` | Turso database connection |\n63\t| `TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN` | Turso auth |\n64\t| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | GPT-4o Vision analysis |\n65\t| `AUTH_SECRET` | NextAuth session encryption |\n66\t| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | Google OAuth |\n67\t| `GITHUB_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | GitHub OAuth |\n68\t| `RESEND_API_KEY` | Email notifications |\n69\t\n70\t## Testing\n71\t\n72\t```bash\n73\tnpm test              # Run all tests (29 tests, 3 suites)\n74\t```\n75\t\n76\tTests cover: vision JSON parsing, notification thresholds, plan limits, structured diff logic, compliance action filters, rate limiting, schema sync between engine and app.\n77\t\n78\t## Production monitoring\n79\t\n80\t- **CI:** Tests + build run on every push\n81\t- **Uptime:** Health checks every 5 minutes, email alerts on downtime\n82\t- **DB backup:** Daily export to GitHub Actions artifacts (30 day retention)\n83\t- **Crash alerts:** Engine emails on fatal errors\n84\t- **Rate limiting:** All public API endpoints (60 req/min)\n85\t- **Health:** `GET /api/health` returns DB status + env check\n86\t\n87\t## API (Pro+)\n88\t\n89\t```bash\n90\t# List your changes\n91\tcurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer cb_...\" https://app.changebrief.io/api/v1/changes\n92\t\n93\t# Filter by compliance action\n94\tcurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer cb_...\" \"https://app.changebrief.io/api/v1/changes?action=action_required\"\n95\t\n96\t# List monitored sources\n97\tcurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer cb_...\" https://app.changebrief.io/api/v1/sources\n98\t```\n99\t\n100\t## Plans\n101\t\n102\t| | Free | Pro | Team |\n103\t|---|---|---|---|\n104\t| Monitored pages | 3 | 25 | 100 |\n105\t| Checks/month | 100 | 2,000 | 10,000 |\n106\t| History retention | 7 days | 90 days | 365 days |\n107\t| API access | - | Yes | Yes |\n108\t| Teams/Discord/PagerDuty | - | Yes | Yes |\n109\t| Team assignment | - | - | Yes |\n110\t\n111\t## Deploy\n112\t\n113\t```bash\n114\t# Landing page → Cloudflare Pages\n115\tcd landing && npm run build && npx wrangler pages deploy dist --project-name pagewatch\n116\t\n117\t# App → Vercel\n118\tcd app && npx vercel --prod --yes\n119\t\n120\t# Trigger engine manually\n121\tgh workflow run check-urls.yml\n122\t```\n123\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"280bf1c5-ae85-4b13-bbe8-9cde344420de","uuid":"e7c57622-5838-4607-8126-cb8fd0ebf24b","timestamp":"2026-04-18T21:22:33.202Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/wigclaw/overnight-work/changebrief-night-improve/README.md","content":"# changebrief\n\nAI-powered regulatory monitoring. Watches government and agency websites, detects changes, and tells you *what* changed — not just that something changed.\n\n> \"Finansinspektionen published new capital adequacy requirements for credit institutions. Effective 2026-06-01.\"\n\n**Live:** [changebrief.io](https://changebrief.io) | **App:** [app.changebrief.io](https://app.changebrief.io) | **Status:** [app.changebrief.io/status](https://app.changebrief.io/status)\n\n## How it works\n\n1. **Playwright** screenshots each monitored page every 6 hours\n2. **Pixelmatch** compares with previous screenshot (cheap pixel filter)\n3. If change > threshold → **GPT-4o Vision** analyzes what changed\n4. AI classifies regulatory changes: `action_required`, `review_recommended`, or `info_only`\n5. Notifications via email, Slack, Teams, Discord, PagerDuty, or webhook\n\n## Architecture\n\n```\nlanding/          — Astro + Tailwind → Cloudflare Pages (changebrief.io)\napp/              — Next.js (App Router) + Auth.js → Vercel (app.changebrief.io)\nengine/           — Playwright + GPT-4o Vision → GitHub Actions (cron every 6h)\nshared/           — Shared logic (diff, vision, notify, schema)\ntests/            — Vitest test suite\n```\n\n| Component | Tech | Where |\n|---|---|---|\n| Landing page | Astro + Tailwind | Cloudflare Pages |\n| Web app | Next.js, Auth.js, Turso | Vercel |\n| Database | Turso (libsql, eu-west-1) | AWS Ireland |\n| Engine | Playwright, Pixelmatch, OpenAI | GitHub Actions |\n| Billing | Polar.sh + Stripe | External |\n| Email | Resend | External |\n\n## Getting started\n\n```bash\n# 1. Clone and install\ngit clone https://github.com/TWINDEJ/changebrief.git\ncd changebrief\nnpm install\nnpx playwright install chromium\n\n# 2. Configure\ncp .env.example .env\n# Fill in all required variables (see .env.example for details)\n\n# 3. Run the app locally\ncd app && npm install && npm run dev\n\n# 4. Run the engine manually\nnpx ts-node engine/check-all.ts\n```\n\n## Environment variables\n\nSee `.env.example` for the complete list. Required:\n\n| Variable | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `TURSO_DATABASE_URL` | Turso database connection |\n| `TURSO_AUTH_TOKEN` | Turso auth |\n| `OPENAI_API_KEY` | GPT-4o Vision analysis |\n| `AUTH_SECRET` | NextAuth session encryption |\n| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | Google OAuth |\n| `GITHUB_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | GitHub OAuth |\n| `RESEND_API_KEY` | Email notifications |\n\n## Testing\n\n```bash\nnpm test              # Run all tests (29 tests, 3 suites)\n```\n\nTests cover: vision JSON parsing, notification thresholds, plan limits, structured diff logic, compliance action filters, rate limiting, schema sync between engine and app.\n\n## Production monitoring\n\n- **CI:** Tests + build run on every push\n- **Uptime:** Health checks every 5 minutes, email alerts on downtime\n- **DB backup:** Daily export to GitHub Actions artifacts (30 day retention)\n- **Crash alerts:** Engine emails on fatal errors\n- **Rate limiting:** All public API endpoints (60 req/min)\n- **Health:** `GET /api/health` returns DB status + env check\n\n## API (Pro+)\n\n```bash\n# List your changes\ncurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer cb_...\" https://app.changebrief.io/api/v1/changes\n\n# Filter by compliance action\ncurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer cb_...\" \"https://app.changebrief.io/api/v1/changes?action=action_required\"\n\n# List monitored sources\ncurl -H \"Authorization: Bearer cb_...\" https://app.changebrief.io/api/v1/sources\n```\n\n## Plans\n\n| | Free | Pro | Team |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Monitored pages | 3 | 25 | 100 |\n| Checks/month | 100 | 2,000 | 10,000 |\n| History retention | 7 days | 90 days | 365 days |\n| API access | - | Yes | Yes |\n| Teams/Discord/PagerDuty | - | Yes | Yes |\n| Team assignment | - | - | Yes |\n\n## Deploy\n\n```bash\n# Landing page → Cloudflare Pages\ncd landing && npm run build && npx wrangler pages deploy dist --project-name pagewatch\n\n# App → Vercel\ncd app && npx vercel --prod --yes\n\n# Trigger engine manually\ngh workflow run check-urls.yml\n```\n","numLines":123,"startLine":1,"totalLines":123}}}
