i' : 'DPA & SLA guarantee'}</li>\n214\t                <li class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><svg class=\"h-4 w-4 shrink-0 text-emerald-500\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M5 13l4 4L19 7\" /></svg>{lang === 'sv' ? 'Fakturering' : 'Invoice billing'}</li>\n215\t              </ul>\n216\t              <a href=\"mailto:kristian@changebrief.io?subject=Enterprise%20inquiry\" class=\"btn-glow mt-8 block rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-blue-600 py-3 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer\">{lang === 'sv' ? 'Kontakta oss' : 'Contact us'}</a>\n217\t            </div>\n218\t          </div>\n219\t        </div>\n220\t      </div>\n221\t    </section>\n222\t\n223\t    <!-- FAQ -->\n224\t    <section class=\"relative py-24 lg:py-32 theme-bg-secondary border-t theme-border\">\n225\t      <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6\">\n226\t        <h2 class=\"animate-fade-in-up text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight theme-text sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">{lt('faq.h2', lang)}</h2>\n227\t        <div class=\"mt-12 space-y-4\">\n228\t          {['1','2','3','4'].map(n => (\n229\t            <details class=\"group animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-6 cursor-pointer\">\n230\t              <summary class=\"flex items-center justify-between font-semibold theme-text [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n231\t                {lt(`faq.q${n}` as any, lang)}\n232\t                <svg class=\"h-5 w-5 shrink-0 theme-text-muted transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" /></svg>\n233\t              </summary>\n234\t              <p class=\"mt-4 text-sm theme-text-secondary leading-relaxed\">{lt(`faq.a${n}` as any, lang)}</p>\n235\t            </details>\n236\t          ))}\n237\t        </div>\n238\t      </div>\n239\t    </section>\n240\t  </main>\n241\t\n242\t  <!-- Footer CTA -->\n243\t  <section class=\"relative py-24 lg:py-32 border-t theme-border\">\n244\t    <div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 text-center\">\n245\t      <h2 class=\"animate-fade-in-up text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight theme-text sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">\n246\t        {lt('footer.h2a', lang)}<br class=\"hidden sm:block\" /> {lt('footer.h2b', lang)} <span class=\"text-gradient\">{lt('footer.h2c', lang)}</span>\n247\t      </h2>\n248\t      <p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl animate-fade-in-up text-lg theme-text-secondary\">{lt('footer.sub', lang)}</p>\n249\t      <a href=\"https://app.changebrief.io\" class=\"btn-glow mt-8 inline-flex animate-fade-in-up items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer\">\n250\t        {lt('footer.cta', lang)}\n251\t        <svg class=\"h-4 w-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6\" /></svg>\n252\t      </a>\n253\t    </div>\n254\t  </section>\n255\t  <footer class=\"border-t theme-border py-12\">\n256\t    <div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center gap-6 px-6 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between\">\n257\t      <div class=\"flex items-center gap-2.5 text-lg font-bold\">\n258\t        <div class=\"flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-indigo-600\">\n259\t          <svg class=\"h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.5\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\" /><path d=\"M2 12s4-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-4 7-10 7-10-7-10-7z\" /></svg>\n260\t        </div>\n261\t        <span class=\"theme-text\">change<span class=\"text-blue-600\">brief</span></span>\n262\t      </div>\n263\t      <nav class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-sm theme-text-muted\">\n264\t        <a href={lang === 'sv' ? '/sv/security' : '/security'} class=\"transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] cursor-pointer\">{lang === 'sv' ? 'Säkerhet' : 'Security'}</a>\n265\t        <a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] cursor-pointer\">{lang === 'sv' ? 'Integritetspolicy' : 'Privacy'}</a>\n266\t        <a href=\"/terms\" class=\"transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] cursor-pointer\">{lang === 'sv' ? 'Villkor' : 'Terms'}</a>\n267\t        <a href=\"/dpa\" class=\"transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] cursor-pointer\">DPA</a>\n268\t        <a href=\"mailto:kristian@changebrief.io\" class=\"transition-colors duration-200 hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] cursor-pointer\">{lt('footer.contact', lang)}</a>\n269\t      </nav>\n270\t      <p class=\"text-sm theme-text-muted\">&copy; 2026 changebrief</p>\n271\t    </div>\n272\t  </footer>\n273\t</Base>\n274\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"280bf1c5-ae85-4b13-bbe8-9cde344420de","uuid":"6001edf7-9194-44a3-a161-1e1cd73a0922","timestamp":"2026-04-18T21:22:41.951Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/wigclaw/overnight-work/changebrief-night-improve/landing/src/components/LandingPage.astro","content":"---\nimport Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';\nimport Header from './Header.astro';\nimport { lt, type Lang } from '../i18n';\n\ninterface Props { lang: Lang }\nconst { lang } = Astro.props;\n\nconst title = lang === 'sv'\n  ? 'changebrief — Se vad som ändrades, inte bara att något ändrades'\n  : 'changebrief — See what changed, not just that something changed';\nconst description = lt('hero.sub', lang);\n\nconst canonical = lang === 'sv'\n  ? 'https://changebrief.io/sv'\n  : 'https://changebrief.io';\n\nconst hreflang = [\n  { lang: 'en', href: 'https://changebrief.io' },\n  { lang: 'sv', href: 'https://changebrief.io/sv' },\n  { lang: 'x-default', href: 'https://changebrief.io' },\n];\n\nconst structuredData = {\n  '@context': 'https://schema.org',\n  '@type': 'WebApplication',\n  name: 'changebrief',\n  url: 'https://changebrief.io',\n  applicationCategory: 'BusinessApplication',\n  operatingSystem: 'Web',\n  description: lang === 'sv'\n    ? 'changebrief bevakar webbsidor och berättar med AI vad som ändrades — inte bara att något ändrades.'\n    : 'changebrief monitors web pages and uses AI to tell you exactly what changed — not just that something changed.',\n  offers: {\n    '@type': 'Offer',\n    price: '0',\n    priceCurrency: 'USD',\n  },\n};\n---\n\n<Base title={title} description={description} lang={lang} canonical={canonical} hreflang={hreflang} structuredData={structuredData}>\n  <Header lang={lang} />\n  <main>\n    <!-- Hero -->\n    <section class=\"relative overflow-hidden pt-36 pb-24 lg:pt-44 lg:pb-36 theme-bg\">\n      <div class=\"relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 text-center\">\n        <div class=\"mb-8 inline-flex animate-fade-in-up items-center gap-2.5 rounded-full bg-blue-50 border border-blue-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm text-blue-700\">\n          <span class=\"relative flex h-2 w-2\"><span class=\"absolute inline-flex h-full w-full animate-ping rounded-full bg-blue-500 opacity-60\"></span><span class=\"relative inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-blue-500\"></span></span>\n          {lt('hero.badge', lang)}\n        </div>\n        <h1 class=\"mx-auto max-w-4xl animate-fade-in-up delay-100 text-5xl font-extrabold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight theme-text sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl\">\n          {lt('hero.h1a', lang)}\n          <span class=\"block text-gradient\">{lt('hero.h1b', lang)}</span>\n        </h1>\n        <p class=\"mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl animate-fade-in-up delay-200 text-lg leading-relaxed theme-text-secondary lg:text-xl\">\n          <span class=\"theme-text font-semibold\">change</span><span class=\"text-blue-600 font-semibold\">brief</span> {lang === 'sv' ? 'bevakar webbsidor och berättar med AI exakt vad som hände. Inga suddiga screenshots. Inga röda pixlar. Bara en tydlig mening.' : 'monitors web pages and uses AI to tell you exactly what happened. No blurry screenshots. No red pixels. Just a clear sentence.'}\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"mt-10 flex animate-fade-in-up delay-300 flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row\">\n          <a href=\"https://app.changebrief.io\" class=\"btn-glow group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300\">\n            {lt('hero.cta1', lang)}\n            <svg class=\"h-4 w-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6\" /></svg>\n          </a>\n          <a href=\"#how-it-works\" class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border theme-border theme-bg px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-semibold theme-text-secondary transition-all duration-200 hover:border-slate-300 hover:text-[var(--text-primary)] hover:shadow-sm\">\n            {lt('hero.cta2', lang)}\n            <svg class=\"h-4 w-4 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover:translate-y-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\" /></svg>\n          </a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- How it works -->\n    <section id=\"how-it-works\" class=\"relative py-24 lg:py-32 border-t theme-border\">\n      <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6\">\n        <div class=\"text-center animate-fade-in-up\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight theme-text sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">{lt('how.h2', lang)}</h2>\n          <p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg theme-text-secondary\">{lt('how.sub', lang)}</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3\">\n          {[['s1', 'link'], ['s2', 'camera'], ['s3', 'bulb']].map(([key]) => (\n            <div class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8\">\n              <div class=\"mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-50 text-blue-600\">\n                <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z\" /></svg>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"mb-2 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-blue-600/70\">{lt(`how.${key}` as any, lang)}</div>\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold theme-text\">{lt(`how.${key}.h` as any, lang)}</h3>\n              <p class=\"mt-2 theme-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">{lt(`how.${key}.p` as any, lang)}</p>\n            </div>\n          ))}\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Use Cases -->\n    <section class=\"relative py-24 lg:py-32 theme-bg-secondary border-t theme-border\">\n      <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6\">\n        <div class=\"text-center animate-fade-in-up\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight theme-text sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">{lt('use.h2', lang)}</h2>\n          <p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg theme-text-secondary\">{lt('use.sub', lang)}</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mt-16 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3\">\n          <div class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 cursor-default\">\n            <div class=\"mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600\">\n              <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" /></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold theme-text\">{lt('use.comp.h', lang)}</h3>\n            <p class=\"mt-3 theme-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">{lt('use.comp.p', lang)}</p>\n          </div>\n          <a href={lang === 'sv' ? '/sv/compliance' : '/compliance'} class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 group ring-2 ring-red-200 bg-red-50/30\">\n            <div class=\"mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-red-50 text-red-600\">\n              <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3\" /></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold theme-text\">{lt('use.reg.h', lang)}</h3>\n            <p class=\"mt-3 theme-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">{lt('use.reg.p', lang)}</p>\n            <span class=\"mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-red-600 group-hover:text-red-700 transition\">\n              {lang === 'sv' ? 'Se compliance-lösning' : 'See compliance solution'}\n              <svg class=\"h-4 w-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6\" /></svg>\n            </span>\n          </a>\n          <div class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 cursor-default\">\n            <div class=\"mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-50 text-amber-600\">\n              <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z\" /></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold theme-text\">{lt('use.vendor.h', lang)}</h3>\n            <p class=\"mt-3 theme-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">{lt('use.vendor.p', lang)}</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 cursor-default\">\n            <div class=\"mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-purple-50 text-purple-600\">\n              <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z\" /></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold theme-text\">{lt('use.hiring.h', lang)}</h3>\n            <p class=\"mt-3 theme-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">{lt('use.hiring.p', lang)}</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 cursor-default\">\n            <div class=\"mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600\">\n              <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M16 11V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4M5 9h14l1 12H4L5 9z\" /></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold theme-text\">{lt('use.ecom.h', lang)}</h3>\n            <p class=\"mt-3 theme-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">{lt('use.ecom.p', lang)}</p>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-8 cursor-default\">\n            <div class=\"mb-5 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-cyan-50 text-cyan-600\">\n              <svg class=\"h-6 w-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z\" /></svg>\n            </div>\n            <h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold theme-text\">{lt('use.site.h', lang)}</h3>\n            <p class=\"mt-3 theme-text-secondary text-[15px] leading-relaxed\">{lt('use.site.p', lang)}</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Pricing -->\n    <section id=\"pricing\" class=\"relative py-24 lg:py-32 border-t theme-border\">\n      <div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6\">\n        <div class=\"text-center animate-fade-in-up\">\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight theme-text sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl\">{lt('price.h2', lang)}</h2>\n          <p class=\"mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg theme-text-secondary\">{lt('price.sub', lang)}</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mt-16 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-4\">\n          <!-- Free -->\n          <div class=\"animate-fade-in-up glass-card rounded-2xl p-7 flex flex-col\">\n            <h3 class=\"text-lg font-semibold theme-text-muted\">Free</h3>\n            <div class=\"mt-4 flex items-baseline gap-1\"><span class=\"text-4xl font-bold theme-text\">$0</span><span class=\"theme-text-muted\">{lt('price.mo', lang)}</span><